page_0: "Oh what am I to do! Six bookings cancelled and I still have no idea when these villains are going to leave! I managed to secure the Blackbrook Philharmonic recording before the looting started. Luckily it seems these uncultured fools have little appreciation of the value of such an exquisite recording and as such, I may yet turn a profit. At least if this castle doesn't descend any further into insanity! 
Oh good, I'm to be traded for supplies. The chances of me being horribly murdered would seem to be dwindling."
